Hello, all.

First thing I'm wondering: Do you need to refrence a set universe, like Doctor Who or Star Trek, or can you use your own universe? (Provided you have a LOT of backstory, which I do... )

If so, Aurerra sends its greetings. Aurerra was discovered in 2680 AD, and was immediately targeted by the International Spaceflight Association as a habitable planet. Earth was running low on resources: the asteroid mining companies had not proved as profitable as once thought, and the other planets yielded little to no success. Aurerra was rich in resources, having an abundance of metals, and as such was decided as the site of a planetwide mining operation. Settled by Earth in the year 2766, six interplanetary freighters travel to and from the Aberats-1 system and Earth, bringing new settlers and supplies to Aurerra, while the settlements of Aurerra send up raw materials to bring back home.
